        Constructs the analysis manager.
        Parameters:
        operatingSystem - the name of the operating system on which the tool is currently executed
        versionControlSystem - the name of the version control system from which the commits are extracted
        analysisProperties - the properties of the properties file defining the analysis process and the configuration of the analyzer in use; all properties, which start with the prefix "analysis."
        commitQueue - the CommitQueue for requesting extracted commits
